            . I am an officer, I was informed of this; about ten days afterwards I saw the prisoner at the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182602160058"></xptr>Ball and Horse Shoe, public-house, in Westminster; he asked how I did - and I inquired if he had made all right with his master - he said, No - and I took him.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 20.</p>
